# 🧠 1. What Nx cache actually does

Nx Remote Cache:

> “If I already ran this exact task with the same inputs, I reuse the result.”

It affects only:

* build speed ⚡
* test speed ⚡
* lint speed ⚡

It does NOT affect:

* which code is tested ❌
* which code is deployed ❌
