Cache becomes unsafe only if YOU break assumptions:

## ❌ Dangerous patterns:

* writing random files outside build folder
* using timestamps in builds
* non-deterministic scripts

Example:

```bash id="bad2"
echo "build time: $(date)" > output.txt
```

👉 This breaks caching reliability

