👉 Even if parts were inspected before, final inspection still happens.

---

# ⚠️ 9. Why this is safe (important truth)

Nx cache CANNOT:

* skip tests on changed code ❌
* deploy untested code ❌
* bypass CI logic ❌

It only:

* reduces repetition of identical work

---

# 🏁 10. Final “big company” rule

> “We trust cache for speed, but we trust CI for truth.”

